      "createdAt": "2022-10-26T06:35:05.237Z",
      "author": "DanielSmith-IOI (Daniel Smith (IOI / BPX))",
      "cookedHtml": "<p>Hi Ellen,</p>\n<p>You can embed forms you’ve created in <a href=\"http://monday.com\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">monday.com</a> by going to the Share form link:<br />\n</p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/2X/4/4e6719cd2f69b0bb7f9e70f6cf680ed150ac9bf4.png\" title=\"01 - share form\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/2X/4/4e6719cd2f69b0bb7f9e70f6cf680ed150ac9bf4_2_690x255.png\" alt=\"01 - share form\" width=\"690\" height=\"255\" /><div class=\"meta\">\n<span class=\"filename\">01 - share form</span><span class=\"informations\">2922×1080 152 KB</span>\n</div></a></div><p></p>\n<p>You can then click on the embed option in the new window that appears:<br />\n</p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/2X/9/989f0f2f0f5830eeaa190b549e2790f895382465.png\" title=\"02 - embed option\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/2X/9/989f0f2f0f5830eeaa190b549e2790f895382465_2_690x343.png\" alt=\"02 - embed option\" width=\"690\" height=\"343\" /><div class=\"meta\">\n<span class=\"filename\">02 - embed option</span><span class=\"informations\">3354×1668 348 KB</span>\n</div></a></div><p></p>\n<p>Once you’ve clicked on that, you will get an embed link which you can copy and use in your site:<br />\n</p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/2X/2/2267f7019141ad43cd0a3e7b782265a7fab706b4.jpeg\" title=\"03 - embed link\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/2X/2/2267f7019141ad43cd0a3e7b782265a7fab706b4_2_690x333.jpeg\" alt=\"03 - embed link\" width=\"690\" height=\"333\" /><div class=\"meta\">\n<span class=\"filename\">03 - embed link</span><span class=\"informations\">3360×1622 252 KB</span>\n</div></a></div><p></p>\n<p>All the best,<br />\nDaniel</p>"
